For the past 5 years, we have carefully gathered a community of people that have manually assembled our WiFi database by constantly adding and updating information. 

More than 50 million people around the world have added over 7 million WiFi hotspots. That's why we have so many hotspots in every corner of the planet. 

Every day we send out an update for WiFi passwords in your area, you can download it under the tab “Update Passwords”. 

We also try to motivate our users by giving them points for adding a new WiFi hotspot (100 points) and updating passwords on the existing hotspots (50 points).

More than 50 million people around the world have added over 7 million WiFi hotspots. That's why we have so many hotspots in every corner of the planet.

We also try to motivate our users by giving them points for adding a new WiFi hotspot (100 points) and updating passwords on the existing hotspots (50 points).
